Package: splithalfr
Title: Extensible Bootstrapped Split-Half Reliabilities
Version: 1.0.9
Author: Thomas Pronk [aut, cre]
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Pronk", email = "pronkthomas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates scores and estimates bootstrapped split-half reliabilities for reaction time tasks and questionnaires. The splithalfr can be extended with custom scoring algorithms for user-provided datasets.
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
License: GPL-3
